The paper deals with subspace identification, which is a topic in control systems (cs.SY). The use of nuclear norm minimization is a common technique in machine learning and optimization (cs.LG), and the paper also mentions the integration of a classical prediction error cost function, which is a common approach in numerical analysis (cs.NA).
